edu.cnm.deepdive.picturequest.model.dao

Interface InputDao


  • public interface InputDao
    Dao Interface designed to interact with the Input Entity of the database, containing method to Insert, get all Input, get t Input for a specific Scene and to delete Input stored for a specific Player and Scene
    Author:
    Brian Alexander
